OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778771468
OL,3,CMan guilty of shotgun shooting at
OL,4,Cwake, killing cousin and injuring
OL,5,Cbrother
OL,7,FA mentally unwell man has been found
OL,8,Fguilty of shooting his cousin dead and
OL,9,Finjuring his brother at a family wake.
OL,11,FJahmel Joseph, 29, blasted Jordan
OL,12,FRodney in the eye then hit his brother
OL,13,FOmar Joseph in the head and hand at a
OL,14,Fgathering in Hammersmith, west London,
OL,15,Fon June 11 2025.
OL,17,FThe next day, Joseph, who has
OL,18,Fschizophrenia, sped away from police,
OL,19,Fcrashed his Mercedes into multiple
OL,20,Fcars and then ran through gardens to
OL,21,Fevade arrest.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
