OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778771468
OL,3,CMan guilty of shotgun shooting at
OL,4,Cwake, killing cousin and injuring
OL,5,Cbrother
OL,7,FIn his defence, Joseph claimed that in
OL,8,Fhis psychotic state he feared Mr
OL,9,FRodney and then his family and police
OL,10,Fwould kill him.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, Joseph, from Ealing, was
OL,13,Ffound guilty of murder, attempted
OL,14,Fmurder, having a firearm with intent
OL,15,Fto endanger life, dangerous driving
OL,16,Fand possessing a shotgun.
OL,18,FPreviously, the Old Bailey heard Mr
OL,19,FRodney, 30, had been arguing with
OL,20,FJoseph at the wake, with the defendant
OL,21,Fcomplaining he had not been sleeping.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778771468
OL,3,CMan guilty of shotgun shooting at
OL,4,Cwake, killing cousin and injuring
OL,5,Cbrother
OL,7,FA relative then told the pair to keep
OL,8,Fthe noise down before telling Joseph
OL,9,Fto go home.
OL,11,FHe later got on his Yamaha motorcycle
OL,12,Farmed with a shotgun and returned to
OL,13,Fthe wake just before midnight.
OL,15,FMr Rodney was shot at close range in
OL,16,Fthe eye and the defendant's brother,
OL,17,Fwho survived, turned his head
OL,18,Finstinctively at the sound and put his
OL,19,Fhand up to protect his face.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
