OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778771468
OL,3,CMan guilty of shotgun shooting at
OL,4,Cwake, killing cousin and injuring
OL,5,Cbrother
OL,7,FAfter the shooting, Joseph returned
OL,8,Fhome and drove his Mercedes car to a
OL,9,Fservice station in Buckinghamshire
OL,10,Fwhere he bought a coffee.
OL,12,FHe went home in the early hours of
OL,13,FJune 12 and had a "bonfire" in the
OL,14,Fgarden, the court was told.
OL,16,FLater that morning, Mr Rodney's mother
OL,17,F` Joseph's aunt ` called the defendant
OL,18,Fand accused him of killing her son.
OL,20,FJoseph denied it and told her: "I did
OL,21,Fnot do that ` I was at home sleeping."
OL,26,@uD@SOUuD@[O]|D@`OU}D@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778771468
OL,3,CMan guilty of shotgun shooting at
OL,4,Cwake, killing cousin and injuring
OL,5,Cbrother
OL,7,FBy the time Joseph left his flat
OL,8,Fagain, at around 6.20am, police were
OL,9,Flooking for him.
OL,11,FHis Mercedes was spotted in Isleworth
OL,12,Fand Joseph sped away with police in
OL,13,Fpursuit.
OL,15,FProsecutor Crispin Aylett KC had said:
OL,16,F"In the course of the chase that
OL,17,Ffollowed, the defendant's car struck a
OL,18,Fnumber of other vehicles. In all,
OL,19,Fabout 20 cars sustained differing
OL,20,Flevels of damage."
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
