OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778771468
OL,3,CMan guilty of shotgun shooting at
OL,4,Cwake, killing cousin and injuring
OL,5,Cbrother
OL,7,FThe chase ended when Joseph's Mercedes
OL,8,Fcollided head-on with another car and
OL,9,Fcame to a stop.
OL,11,FJoseph abandoned the vehicle and fled
OL,12,Fon foot through neighbouring gardens
OL,13,Funtil he was eventually arrested in a
OL,14,Fgarden.
OL,16,FOfficers recovered a sawn-off shotgun
OL,17,Fwith the defendant's DNA on it inside
OL,18,Fa black bag Joseph had thrown away
OL,19,Fduring the chase.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
