OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778771468
OL,3,CMan guilty of shotgun shooting at
OL,4,Cwake, killing cousin and injuring
OL,5,Cbrother
OL,7,FJurors were told Joseph had been
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with paranoid schizophrenia
OL,9,Fand was prescribed medication for it.
OL,11,FHis case was that he was unwell at the
OL,12,Ftime of the shooting and acted as he
OL,13,Fdid under the "reasonable belief" that
OL,14,Fhe feared Mr Rodney would kill him.
OL,16,FThe jury rejected his explanation
OL,17,Fafter deliberating for just nine hours.
OL,19,FJoseph was remanded into custody to be
OL,20,Fsentenced on a later date.
OL,26,@uD@OOUuD@aO]
